# Testing Standards

- TDD for `packages/domain`: failing test → implement → pass → commit
- Appendix A golden fixtures are normative (not optional)
- Test names include PRD IDs: `'BB-CALC-01: cost 150 for Highest+Critical'`
- Domain tests: no mocks. Integration tests: Supabase local.
- Coverage: 100% domain, 80% infra/API
